reviews.review_text: Texas Dead Nice job of putting this one together!  Just the right amount of audience noise.  Captures the excitement of the show without distracting from the actual music from soundboard.  Show features the band's 1st live performance of "Built to Last".  A couple of small audience patches at beginning of "Queen Jane" and "Miracle" that were mixed in nicely.  Good performance of "Playin'...:".  Enjoyed this one!  Thanks for the upload!
